y\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.fda.gov/media/137564/download\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"content-link css-5r4717\"\u003eissued an order\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/hl-trusted-source\u003e on May 1 for the emergency use of remdesivir."},{"tagName":"p","source":"\u003cstrong\u003eKaletra\u003c/strong\u003e"},{"tagName":"p","source":"This is a combination of two drugs \u0026mdash; lopinavir and ritonavir \u0026mdash; that work against HIV. \u003ca href=\"https://news.abbvie.com/news/press-releases/abbvie-partnering-with-global-authorities-to-determine-efficacy-hiv-drug-in-treating-covid-19.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"content-link css-5r4717\"\u003eClinical trials\u003c/a\u003e are being done to see whether it also works against SARS-CoV-2."},{"tagName":"p","source":"One small \u003ca href=\"https://www.cell.com/med/fulltext/S2666-6340(20)30001-5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"content-link css-5r4717\"\u003estudy\u003c/a\u003e published May 4 in the journal Med by Cell Press found that lopinavir/ritonavir did not improve outcomes in people with mild or moderate COVID-19 compared to those receiving standard care."},{"tagName":"p","source":"Another \u003ca href=\"https://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMoa2001282\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"content-link css-5r4717\"\u003estudy\u003c/a\u003e, published May 7 in the New England Journal of Medicine, found that the drug combination was not effective for people with severe COVID-19."},{"tagName":"p","source":"But another study found that people who were given lopinavir/ritonavir along with two other drugs \u0026mdash; ribavirin and interferon beta-1b \u0026mdash; took less time to clear the virus from their body. This study was \u003chl-trusted-source source=\"The Lancet\" rationale=\"Highly respected journal,Expert written journal,Peer reviewed journal\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.thelancet.com/journals/lancet/a